{"id":1055,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":21,"title":"Conversation 11","subtitle":"Restaurant Reservation Call","level":"B1","parts":12,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-11.1055/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-11-2023-09-11-16-36-43/0-conversation-11.mp3","transcript":"Hello, Osaka Today Restaurant.\nHow may I help you?\nHi, I'd like to make a reservation for 3 for 6 o'clock this Saturday in the name of Josh Price.\nI'm afraid we're fully booked at that time.\nCould an earlier or later time suit you?\nI can fit you in at 5 or 7:30.\nWell, 5 o'clock is a bit early for dinner.\nLet's make it 7:30 then.\nI might have to get back to you because I'm not too sure.\nNo problem, Mr. Price.\nYour table will be kept for 15 minutes.\nMay I also have your phone number, please?","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:59:42","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hello, Osaka Today Restaurant.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-11-2023-09-11-16-36-43/1.mp3","time_start":0.12,"time_end":2.73},{"position":2,"content":"How may I help you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-11-2023-09-11-16-36-43/2.mp3","time_start":2.73,"time_end":4.03},{"position":3,"content":"Hi, I'd like to make a reservation for 3 for 6 o'clock this Saturday in the name of Josh Price.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-11-2023-09-11-16-36-43/3.mp3","time_start":4.03,"time_end":12.16},{"position":4,"content":"I'm afraid we're fully booked at that time.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-11-2023-09-11-16-36-43/4.mp3","time_start":12.16,"time_end":14.8},{"position":5,"content":"Could an earlier or later time suit you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-11-2023-09-11-16-36-43/5.mp3","time_start":14.8,"time_end":17.29},{"posit